## Examples  
 下列範例會搜尋給定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>，並顯示<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A>和<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Parent%2A>的結果。  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _   
          "LDAP://onecity/CN=user,CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
