## Remarks  
 您可以設定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A>和<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A>屬性來指定替代的認證，用來存取 Active Directory 網域服務中的資訊。 任何其他<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>從這個執行個體擷取物件 (例如，透過<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>) 會自動建立具有相同的替代認證。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下列範例示範<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A>並<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A>的屬性<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>類別。 這個範例會取得使用者指定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>而<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A>所有其<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>。  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _  
      "LDAP://onecity/CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
' Create an Instance of DirectoryEntry.  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As New DirectoryEntry(myADSPath)  
myDirectoryEntry.Username = UserName  
myDirectoryEntry.Password = SecurelyStoredPassword  
  
' Get the Child ADS objects.  
Console.WriteLine("The Child ADS objects are:")  
Dim myChildDirectoryEntry As DirectoryEntry  
For Each myChildDirectoryEntry In  myDirectoryEntry.Children  
   Console.WriteLine(myChildDirectoryEntry.Path)  
Next myChildDirectoryEntry   
```  
  
```csharp  
